focus on something else, and lis-
tened to the Mexican music, my
number was called. Alert and starv-
ing by this time, I found the journey
to obtain my food quite a struggle
because of the traffic ﬂow. I’m not
going to give Baja a hard time,
though. This is only the first couple
weeks. Things may change.

